| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0888 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7ac35ed5-16f3-5717-b509-bdea944a8d83"
